<br>
Burak explained to the others that he was joining Mensa.  But that two of his alts would be here for the ride.  Then he said, “There are more people not happy with the situation than you can believe. I am constantly getting tells about some absurd comment or another by Xellosx.  As an organizational comment, our leader should be an elected official. One that understands that Kamdar has the power to commandeer the website that we all check. I would like to nominate Wiggam to be our leader. He has shown all the qualities that being a leader are all about. He enjoys attending events and does not gate out at the first sign of trouble. He has been available to help anyone of us in need.  However it shakes out, I would kill to see Xellosx face when he checks the website to find that it now points to a new guild.”<br>
<br>
Arrwen went next, “My thoughts would be not to elect Leaders as they can never be removed. I think the leader should be kept as management purposes only. Where we would rely on our officers for support and later elect them if that is what we desire.  To begin with I think we should decide on set officers. Wiggam certainly would be a choice of mine as well. I think Kamdar since you maintain the site and have a great history with everything you have done, you are my choice as leader. I would if given the task prefer to have Arri (her Alternate and Main character) as an officer as opposed to Arrwen. I have other ideas for people as officers. But first let's see where their interests lie.”<br>
<br>
