<br>
Others agreed that Wiggam or I would be good choices for a leader.<br>
<br>
Wiggam then spoke up, “Let me start by saying I didnt want things to go this way. I think any thoughts of leaving the guild should be discussed in the open with all of the Eternal Stormcallers. But in loyalty to Kamdar and Burak I have to let you folks know what I think.<br>
<br>
